{"tid":182373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插沙]入唔到屋企","createTime":"2017-04-01T09:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T10:41:12.000Z","uid":15453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c96c8ba412a56d0465bc58e94932bf1f49721ebc","tid":182373,"uid":15453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"頭先係走廊整單車<br />\n諗住入屋攞支六角匙<br />\n點知留咗條鎖匙係屋企<br />\n大門無鎖到<br />\n條鎖匙係門口隔離<br />\n但係鐵閘個窿太細<br />\n拎唔到<br />\n鎖匙位置示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/175410_ec6125657c60fa1c1a5dd75135ede433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F175410_ec6125657c60fa1c1a5dd75135ede433.jpg&h=82e525db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家得返電話<br />\n同埋六角匙<br />\n屋企人今晚冇咁快返<br />\n求全能嘅連登仔幫手刷掂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係今晚十二點先有門口入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/175633_8b2c935eaf456cbe2077bb7ba871818f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F175633_8b2c935eaf456cbe2077bb7ba871818f.jpg&h=c2898291&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df04d09e837875faaa1e2f681935cd3424f8ae44","tid":182373,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:02:58.000Z","msg":"踩車出去遊下車河"},{"pid":"1faef6447e6e893e90d2d7f59bf903ff9d9e7393","tid":182373,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:02:59.000Z","msg":"叫人爆鎖"},{"pid":"357416f4db74226da9dc120fa4e3849836e3ee1b","tid":182373,"uid":93460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"問鄰居借個鐵線衫架，拆開佢再拗成一個直角，勾把鎖